==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Hove
<hw>Hove</hw>, <pos>v. i. & t.</pos> <def>To rise; to swell; to heave;
to cause to swell.</def> <mark>[Obs. or Scot.]</mark> <rj><au>Holland.
Burns.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hove</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Hove
<hw>Hove</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[OE. <ets>hoven</ets>. See
<er>Hover</er>.]</ety> <def>To hover around; to loiter; to lurk.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Gower.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

